        "heading_VX6pci": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Grub Control: How to Evict Lawn Pests Before They Move In",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_mBxPfk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A beautiful lawn takes work, but nothing ruins a lush green yard faster than a subterranean grub infestation. When it comes to grubs, timing is absolutely everything. Applying the wrong product at the wrong time is the number one reason lawn treatments fail.<br/><br/>Here is exactly when, what, and how to apply grub treatments to protect your lawn this season.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
